\"to\": 1013, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Frenchman Leo Bergere, who won bronze, then joined the front two on the ground after crossing the line.\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1024, \"end\": 1027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"score\": 0.9538871390399399, \"rank\": 0.045019546792175826, \"text\": \"Leo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yee won a silver medal in the men's triathlon at the delayed Tokyo 2020 Olympics and gold in the mixed relay event.\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And his triumph was seemingly made possible by team-mate Sam Dickinson, who appeared to deliberately push the pace on the bike before retiring.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1292, \"end\": 1305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Dickinson\", \"score\": 0.999985295493271, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Dickinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Dickinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Dickinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6635207107842033e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1570, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9997244036044157, \"rank\": 0.0002756723449549695, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterwards, Yee admitted he thought he was confined to second place.\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have so much respect for Hayden and how much he made me dig in there,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1754, \"end\": 1760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Hayden\", \"score\": 0.9999999998431122, \"rank\": 1.5707731024928445e-10, \"text\": \"Hayden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Hayden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Hayden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was an amazing athlete and for me, almost two laps in I thought that silver was on the cards but I owed it to myself to give myself one last chance.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1962, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With about 2km to go I thought I'd give it everything I had and I am just so proud that I was able to do that for my family, for everyone that's worked hard, for my girlfriend Liv.\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is so many more people than just me who have worked towards this.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This was our dream and I am the lucky one who gets to do it, so thank you to them.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Show your colours and get Team GB's official kit for the Paris Olympics  Do not miss:Team GB snatch second gold in minutes with photo finish in quad sculls rowing  Do not miss:Rafael Nadal hits out at 'totally unnecessary' Olympics rule  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2340, \"end\": 2347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999880033102, \"rank\": 1.1996376742027477e-08, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2490, \"end\": 2502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"I gave it everything I had and I was going through a really bad patch.\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many people have told me that you are gonna go through a bad patch during a race no matter how perfect or bad it is, so I think for me I just rode that wave and said one more try and let us see if we can do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 3079, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's race was initially postponed by 24 hours on Tuesday afterthe water quality in the River Seine failed to meet required standardsfollowing heavy rainfall over the weekend.\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3173, \"end\": 3184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after organisers finally declared the river safe, large crowds in the French capital were treated to two sensational finishes with home favourite Cassandre Beaugrand taking women's gold.\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3411, \"end\": 3430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cassandre_Beaugrand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cassandre Beaugrand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cassandre_Beaugrand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cassandre_Beaugrand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3590, \"end\": 3603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7392800511059114e-24, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3639, \"end\": 3652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7392800511059114e-24, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"